Nuzlocke.content: Any Pokmon that faints is considered dead, and must be released or put in the Pokmon Storage System permanently

The player may only catch the first wild Pokmon encountered in each area, and none else. If the first wild Pokmon encountered faints or flees, there are no second chances. If the first encounter in the area is a double battle, the player is free to choose which of the two wild Pokmon they would like to catch but may only catch one of them.
The player must nickname all of their Pokmon, for the sake of forming stronger emotional bonds
